    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a subphylum including scorpions, spiders, mites, horseshoe crabs, and sea spiders, all of which have six pairs of appendages.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
